Subject:  NorthAmerican Association for the History of the Language Sciences 

	

Full Title: North American Association for the History of the Language Sciences 
Short Title: NAAHoLS 

Date: 03-Jan-2008 - 06-Jan-2008
Location: Chicago, Illinois, USA 
Contact Person: David Boe
Meeting Email: dboe@nmu.edu

Linguistic Field(s): History of Linguistics 

Call Deadline: 01-Sep-2007 

Meeting Description:

North American Association for the History of the Language Sciences meeting 

The 2008 North American Association for the History of the Language Sciences
(NAAHoLS) meeting will again be held in conjunction with the Linguistic Society
of America annual meeting, which will take place at the Palmer House Hilton in
Chicago, 3-6 January 2008. As in the past, we invite papers relating to any
aspect of the history of the language sciences. The deadline for receipt of
500-word abstracts is 1 September 2007 (submitted to dboe@nmu.edu).


 




